    "verdict": "The raw R-vs-log(regulator) correlation is very strong (r ~ -0.75 to -0.85) but is almost entirely a confound: both spectral parameters and regulators scale with level/discriminant. After residualizing on log(level), the partial correlation for the spectral gap drops to r ~ -0.18 (p ~ 0.07), marginal at best. For median R it vanishes entirely. The theoretical connection may exist but is not detectable above the level-scaling confound in this data.",
